- content_for :head
  title SV.CO Talent: Invest &amp Hire
  meta name="description" content="Hire, acqui-hire, invest and build a pipeline from India's best startup talent."
  meta property="og:title" content="SV.CO Talent: Invest & Hire"
  meta property="og:type" content="website"
  meta property="og:url" content=talent_url
  meta property="og:image" content=image_url('shared/logo-color.svg')
  meta property="og:video" content="https://www.youtube.com/v/SWR95X-lmz4"
  meta property="og:description" content="Hire, acqui-hire, invest and build a pipeline from India's best startup talent. Discover great startups for your company, accelerator, or investment fund."
  meta property="fb:app_id" content=Rails.application.secrets.facebook.dig(:app_id)

= render 'invest_hire_form'

.talent-hero
  .container
    .hero-intro.text-xs-center
      h1.talent-hero-headline.letters.talent-hero-headline__type
        span Discover Great Startups for your
        span.hero-words-wrapper
          b.is-visible Investment Fund
          b Company
          b Accelerator
    .tab-container.talent-nav-tab
      ul.nav.nav-tabs.nav-justified role="tablist"
        li.nav-item.talent-tab-item role="presentation"
          a.nav-link.talent-tab-link.active aria-controls="acquihire-teams" data-toggle="tab" href="#acquihire-teams" role="tab"
            .talent-tab-icon.acquihire-team-icon
            span.hidden-xs-down
              | Acquihire Teams
        li.nav-item.talent-tab-item role="presentation"
          a.nav-link.talent-tab-link aria-controls="hire-founders" data-toggle="tab" href="#hire-founders" role="tab"
            .talent-tab-icon.hire-founders-icon
            span.hidden-xs-down
              | Hire Founders
        li.nav-item.talent-tab-item role="presentation"
          a.nav-link.talent-tab-link aria-controls="invest-in-startups" data-toggle="tab" href="#invest-in-startups" role="tab"
            .talent-tab-icon.invest-in-startups-icon
            span.hidden-xs-down
              | Invest in startups
        li.nav-item.talent-tab-item role="presentation"
          a.nav-link.talent-tab-link aria-controls="build-startup-pipeline" data-toggle="tab" href="#build-startup-pipeline" role="tab"
            .talent-tab-icon.accelerate-icon
            span.hidden-xs-down
              | Build a startup pipeline

      .tab-content.talent-tab-content
        #acquihire-teams.tab-pane.fade.in.active role="tabpanel"
          .row
            .col-lg-7.col-md-12
              iframe.talent-video-playlist src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SWR95X-lmz4?list=PLrvZyo34miDJt-m4a0WKUPqMvnmJ-9hVO&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" sandbox="allow-same-origin allow-scripts"
            .col-lg-5.col-md-12
              h3.talent-tab-content__header.font-regular.m-y-1
                ' Companies like <strong>Tally</strong>
                | have acquired founding teams from SV.CO.
              p.font-light
                ' Hiring a team brings you their combined strengths into your company.
                ' Our teams usually have full-stack developers, mobile&#8209;focused engineers and data analysts.
                ' The best part? All of their work is public #{link_to 'through our timelines.', startups_path}
              button.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.talent-action-btn.text-uppercase.m-y-2 data-selection='acquihiring_teams'
                | Acquihire Teams

        #hire-founders.tab-pane.fade.in role="tabpanel"
          .row
            .col-lg-7.col-md-12
              iframe.talent-video-playlist src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cqyOZI4AopI?list=PLrvZyo34miDL8J63zyVLNonPjUK8Q-m6U&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" sandbox="allow-same-origin allow-scripts"
            .col-lg-5.col-md-12
              h3.talent-tab-content__header.font-regular.m-y-1
                ' Companies like <strong>Goqii, Ola &amp; Freecharge</strong>
                | have hired great founders from SV.CO.
              p.font-light
                ' We work with some of the best young founders in India.
                ' Hire Android, iOS &amp; Backend engineers who have built
                ' <em>real products</em> and have industry know&#8209;how. We also
                ' try to match founders&#8217; deep interests with an industry sector
                ' so you get people who are deeply passionate about the work
                | you do.
              button.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.talent-action-btn.m-y-2.text-uppercase data-selection='hiring_founders'
                | Hire Founders
        #invest-in-startups.tab-pane.fade.in role="tabpanel"
          .row
            .col-lg-7.col-md-12
              iframe.talent-video-playlist src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QmavQDI3SV4?list=PLrvZyo34miDIszuU6tptnX5coYUkWVcQi&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" sandbox="allow-same-origin allow-scripts"
            .col-lg-5.col-md-12
              h3.talent-tab-content__header.font-regular.m-y-1
                ' <strong>Fin, Reckone</strong> and <strong>iTraveller</strong>
                | have been funded by amazing investors who are SV.CO partners.
              p.font-light
                ' If you're an angel or seed investor, sign up with us to get access to budding startups.
                | We'll put you in touch early and you can interact with them even as they build their products.
              button.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.talent-action-btn.m-y-2.text-uppercase data-selection='investing_in_startups'
                | Invest in Startups
        #build-startup-pipeline.tab-pane.fade.in role="tabpanel"
          .row
            .col-lg-7.col-md-12
              iframe.talent-video-playlist src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vjDdSdfitKY?enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" sandbox="allow-same-origin allow-scripts"
            .col-lg-5.col-md-12
              h3.talent-tab-content__header.font-regular.m-y-1
                ' Startups like
                ' <strong>Profoundis</strong>
                ' go on to join SV.CO&#8217;s Partner Accelerators.
              p.font-light
                ' If you're an accelerator based in India, get access to our startups to build a
                ' strong pipeline of great companies and get early updates on products our founders are building.
              button.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.talent-action-btn.m-y-2.text-uppercase data-selection='accelerating_startups'
                | Build Startup Pipeline

