.talkto-founders.text-xs-center.p-y-3
  .container
    h2.text-xs-center.font-light.graduate-subhead
      span.graduate-subhead-icon.talkto-graduates-icon
      | Talk to Our Founders Early
    h3
      ' Interact with our student founders &amp; identify great talent
      span.font-weight-400 even while our program is ongoing.

    .talks-ways-container
      .row
        .col-lg-6.talks-ways-section
          .row.talks-ways-section__box
            .col-md-3.col-sm-3.ways-icon.faculty-join-icon
            .col-md-9.col-sm-9.talks-ways-content
              h4.light-secondary.font-regular
                | Join as SV.CO Faculty
              p
                ' A half-hour per week commitment to our collective.
                | Founders send you office hour requests with topics they'd like to discuss about.

        .col-lg-6.talks-ways-section
          .row.talks-ways-section__box
            .col-md-3.col-sm-3.ways-icon.broadcast-icon
            .col-md-9.col-sm-9.talks-ways-content
              h4.light-secondary.font-regular
                | Broadcast to our Collective Live
              p
                ' Present a topic to our Collective or be part of an AMA session with interesting questions from our young
                | founders.
    button.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.talent-action-btn.m-t-2.text-uppercase data-selection='joining_svco_as_faculty'
      | Join as SV.CO Faculty

